### Plotting Figure 1


a. Simulate coordinates of labels on the map

simulate_point_locations.R

requirements:
samples_locations.txt


b. Plot of a map with strains

map_geo.R

requirements:
samples_locations.txt
simulated_coords.txt
world_intermediate.txt


c. Plot of ML phylogeny

plotTree.py

requirements:
Newick_Export_ordered_root_75coll.nwk
Species_distinction_PCA.txt


d. Plot of structure

plotStrcuture.R

requirements:
Structure_genomewide_results_K2.csv
Structure_genomewide_results_novoulmi_K2.csv
Structure_genomewide_results_novoulmi_K3.csv
Species_distinction_PCA.txt


d-e. Plots of PCA

PCA_Plot.R

requirements:
Species_distinction_PCA.txt
scores_pca.txt


